description: City: Pittsburgh, PA Want your tastebuds to travel the world? Look no further than the Burgh's very own Street Foods truck! Their eclectic menu feature the tangy nutty flavors of Thailand's chicken satay, as well as the cheesy breaded goodness of Italy's Arancini balls. Still not convinced? They've also got crispy falafel, the street of Egypt, as well as hearty German bratwurst!
name: Street Foods
